snippet.textDisplay: "Khalasi" is a great example of how music can cross borders. As a Pakistani, it's awesome to see a song that mixes traditional and modern sounds, something we love in Coke Studio Pakistan too. The song feels familiar and new at the same time, reminding us of the shared culture and music heritage between Pakistan and India. It's cool how music can bring people together, showing that despite differences, our love for music is something we all share. Great job on this one!
